      <title>电动汽车制造商获得美国税收抵免资格延长两年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/biden-gives-carmakers-a-break-on-tough-to-trace-ev-materials</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府在最终确定电动汽车税收抵免规则方面给予汽车制造商部分缓刑，旨在放松中国对对汽车行业未来至关重要的电池材料的控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/biden-gives-carmakers-a-break-on-tough-to-trace-ev-materials</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 12:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
