    <item>
      <title>苏纳克在选举中遭受重大打击，但不足以迫使他下台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/uk-local-elections-conservatives-hold-tees-valley-mayoralty-in-relief-for-sunak</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克(Rishi Sunak)领导的执政保守党失去了一个领头羊议会席位，并有望解雇数百名地方议员，这是一系列毁灭性的选举结果，但仍未达到可能促使保守党罢免他的最坏情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/uk-local-elections-conservatives-hold-tees-valley-mayoralty-in-relief-for-sunak</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 11:39:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国谴责俄罗斯对企业和党官员进行网络攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/germany-says-russia-was-behind-cyber-attacks-on-spd-officials</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国表示，现在有明确的证据表明，俄罗斯去年对总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨领导的社会民主党官员以及政府部门和多家公司进行了网络攻击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/germany-says-russia-was-behind-cyber-attacks-on-spd-officials</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 11:15:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加沙抗议投票影响英国工党选举进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/labour-s-uk-election-gains-curbed-by-gaza-protest-votes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工党在英格兰和威尔士地方选举中的强劲表现受到削弱，因为一些穆斯林人口众多的地区的选民似乎不再支持反对党对加沙战争的立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/labour-s-uk-election-gains-curbed-by-gaza-protest-votes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 08:45:53 GMT</pubDate>
